                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              James Cuno, Alvin L. Clark, Jr., Ivan Gaskell, and William W. Robinson, <em>Harvard's Art Museums: 100 Years of Collecting</em>, ed. James Cuno, Harvard University Art Museums and Harry N. Abrams, Inc. (Cambridge, MA, 1996), p. 232, ill. p. 233
                             </p>
